om our Italian headquarters, and PT Dimensi Quantum Wahyudi has been a highly reliable local partner. Their technical support is clear, responsive, and collaborative. Commercially, the proposal offered strong value, and operationally the solution has improved both safety and ergonomics. Installation was smooth from start to finish.","”"],["DIV",{"class":"inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-blue-500/10 border border-blue-500/20 rounded-full px-3 py-1.5 w-fit"},["SPAN",{"class":"w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-cyan-400 shrink-0"}],["SPAN",{"class":"text-cyan-300 text-xs font-bold"},"+40% handling speed"]],["DIV",{"class":"border-t border-white/10 pt-5 flex items-center gap-4"},["DIV",{"class":"relative w-20 h-20 rounded-full overflow-hidden shrink-0 border-2 border-blue-500/40 shadow-[0_0_15px_rgba(59,130,246,0.3)]"},["IMG",{"__playwright_current_src__":"","alt":"Anang Wahyudi","loading":"lazy","decoding":"async","data-nimg":"fill","class":"object-cover","style":"position:absolute;height:100%;width:100%;left:0;top:0;right:0;bottom:0;color:transparent","sizes":"100vw","srcset":"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=640&q=75 640w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=750&q=75 750w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=828&q=75 828w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=1080&q=75 1080w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=1200&q=75 1200w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=1920&q=75 1920w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=2048&q=75 2048w, /_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=3840&q=75 3840w","src":"/_next/image?url=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F2WEnjnU.png&w=3840&q=75"}]],["DIV",{},["P",{"class":"text-white font-bold text-base md:text-lg"},"Anang Wahyudi"],["P",{"class":"text-slate-400 text-sm"},"Project Procurement"],["P",{"class":"text-cyan-400 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-widest mt-1"},"PT